          }
        }
      }
    },
    "二级侧栏支持列表和树状视图切换，既能快速扫列表，也能按目录结构定位。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The secondary sidebar switches between list and tree views for scanning or folder-based navigation."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "二级侧栏支持列表和树状视图切换，既能快速扫列表，也能按目录结构定位。"
          }
