        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "最後設定雲端和偏好"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "底部区域可以进入帮助、设置、切换语言和退出。建议先到设置里填写 IMA Client ID / API Key，并按需配置忽略规则。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The bottom area opens Help, Settings, language switching, and Quit. Fill in IMA Client ID / API Key in Settings and adjust ignore rules as needed."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "底部区域可以进入帮助、设置、切换语言和退出。建议先到设置里填写 IMA Client ID / API Key，并按需配置忽略规则。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "底部區域可以進入幫助、設定、切換語言和退出。建議先到設定裡填寫 IMA Client ID / API Key，並按需配置忽略規則。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
